        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"276037\">Jade Master</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/229136-theory.3A-category.20theory/topic/microcosm.20principle.20for.20actegories/near/232947178\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Similarly for the morphisms. It's morally the same as having objects and morphisms the same as C but now it respects the unit. Is that the problem you were having <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"275901\">Jules Hedges</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Hm, I don't understand this</p>",
